msgstr "Retorna: `string`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:103
msgid "json"
msgstr "json"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:105
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:json`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:json`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:107
msgid "`resp:json()` reads the response body, parses it as JSON, and returns a Lua value."
msgstr "`resp:json()` lĂŞ o corpo da resposta, faz parse como JSON e retorna um valor Lua."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:110
msgid "bytes"
msgstr "bytes"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:112
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:bytes`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:bytes`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:114
msgid "`resp:bytes()` reads and returns the response body as raw bytes."
msgstr "`resp:bytes()` lĂŞ e retorna o corpo da resposta como bytes brutos."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:116
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:116"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "Retorna: `string`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:118
msgid "header"
msgstr "header"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:120
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:header`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:header`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:122
msgid "`resp:header(name)` returns the first response header value matching `name`."
msgstr "`resp:header(name)` retorna o primeiro valor de cabeĂ§alho de resposta que corresponde a `name`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:124
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:124"
msgid "`name` (string, required): The header name to look up."
msgstr "`name` (string, obrigatĂłrio): O nome do cabeĂ§alho a consultar."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:125
msgid "Returns: `string | nil`."
msgstr "Retorna: `string | nil`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:127
msgid "header_values"
msgstr "header_values"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:129
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:header_values`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:header_values`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:131
msgid "`resp:header_values(name)` returns all response header values matching `name`."
msgstr "`resp:header_values(name)` retorna todos os valores de cabeĂ§alho de resposta que correspondem a `name`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:133
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:133"
msgid "`name` (string, required): The header name to look up."
msgstr "`name` (string, obrigatĂłrio): O nome do cabeĂ§alho a consultar."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:134
msgid "Returns: `string[]`."
msgstr "Retorna: `string[]`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:136
msgid "raise_for_status"
msgstr "raise_for_status"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:138
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:raise_for_status`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:raise_for_status`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:140
msgid "`resp:raise_for_status()` raises an error when the response status code is in the 4xx or 5xx range."
msgstr "`resp:raise_for_status()` gera erro quando o cĂłdigo de status da resposta estĂˇ na faixa 4xx ou 5xx."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:143
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:143"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "Notas:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:145
msgid "Non-2xx HTTP statuses do not raise errors by default. Callers can check `resp.ok`, set `fail_on_http_error = true`, or call `resp:raise_for_status()`."
msgstr "Por padrĂŁo, status HTTP fora de 2xx nĂŁo geram erro. Quem chama pode verificar `resp.ok`, definir `fail_on_http_error = true` ou chamar `resp:raise_for_status()`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/http.md:147
msgid "The response body is cached after the first read. Calling `text`, `json`, and `bytes` multiple times is allowed."
msgstr "O corpo da resposta Ă© armazenado em cache apĂłs a primeira leitura, entĂŁo `text`, `json` e `bytes` podem ser chamados vĂˇrias vezes."
